%22%3EJensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2061-year-old%20Silicon%20Valley%20veteran%20running%20Nvidia%20has%20overseen%20a%20%242%20trillion%20surge%20in%20its%20value%20since%20the%20start%20of%20last%20year.%20The%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-news-today-spx-nvidia-price-outlook-record-high-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejourney%20from%20%241%20trillion%20to%20%242%20trillion%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20a%20mere%20nine%20months%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20now%20worth%20%242.35%20trillion%2C%20behind%20only%20Microsoft%20and%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20growth%20story%20has%20a%20simple%20explanation%3A%20Nvidia%20has%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20supplying%20the%20chips%20needed%20to%20power%20the%20generative%20AI%20revolution%2C%20making%20it%20fundamental%20to%20the%20ambitions%20of%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20and%20everyone%20else%20chasing%20AI%20riches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20it's%20little%20wonder%20blowout%20results%20are%20being%20anticipated%20as%20Nvidia%20prepares%20to%20reveal%20its%20first-quarter%20earnings%20after%20the%20bell%20on%20Wednesday.%20As%20Wedbush%20analyst%20Matt%20Bryson%20put%20it%2C%20expect%20a%20%26quot%3Brinse%20and%20repeat%26quot%3B%20of%20recent%20blockbuster%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20a%20CEO%20who%20saw%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-routine-management-leadership-style-ceo-founder-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20bankruptcy%20in%20the%201990s%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Huang%20knows%20that%20success%20isn't%20guaranteed.%20And%20while%20Nvidia%20is%20riding%20high%2C%20challenges%20loom%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc565d20-d22b-4fad-a31d-8e6e43363cb9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENvidia's%20dominance%20faces%20threats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223291%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jensen%20Huang%20presents%20at%20Nvidia's%20GTC%20conference%20in%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f94f634af076d3cf918cc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222332%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJensen%20Huang%20presents%20at%20Nvidia's%20GTC%20conference%20in%202024.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hype%20behind%20Nvidia's%20chips%20is%20no%20joke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Huang%20stood%20onstage%20in%20San%20Jose%20for%20an%20event%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BWoodstock%20of%20AI%26quot%3B%20(he%20seemed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-taylor-swift-nod-shows-aware-of-tech-reputation-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprefer%20the%20comparisons%20to%20Taylor%20Swift%3C%2Fa%3E)%20as%20the%20world%20awaited%20the%20reveal%20of%20Nvidia's%20next-generation%20chips%2C%20or%20GPUs%2C%20dubbed%20Blackwell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackwell%20offers%20technological%20leaps%20over%20its%20predecessor%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20H100%20GPU%20that%20tech%20CEOs%20like%20Zuckerberg%20have%20been%20actively%20seeking%20to%20stockpile%20%E2%80%94%20that%20have%20been%20talked%20up%20in%20the%20industry%20since%20its%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20claimed%20Blackwell%20would%20be%20twice%20as%20powerful%2C%20making%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-gpu-targets-1-8-million-ai-chips-this-year-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20obvious%20purchase%20for%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20seeking%20to%20build%20bigger%2C%20smarter%2C%20more%20efficient%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20competitors%20have%20been%20busy%20developing%20AI%20chips%20of%20their%20own%20to%20reduce%20reliance%20on%20Nvidia's%20increasingly%20expensive%20offerings.%20Price%20estimates%20for%20the%20most%20powerful%20Blackwell%20chip%2C%20the%20GB200%2C%20are%20about%20%2