0Nvidia%20have%20been%20exploring%20Triton%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Ftriton%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoftware%20released%20by%20ChatGPT%20maker%20OpenAI%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20CUDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20succeed%20in%20using%20Triton%2C%20they%20could%20be%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20a%20future%20in%20which%20alternatives%20to%20Nvidia's%20chips%20are%20easier%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPulling%20off%20these%20initiatives%20in%20a%20way%20that%20really%20threatens%20Nvidia%20remains%20some%20way%20off.%20But%20investors%20will%20anxiously%20anticipate%20how%20Nvidia%20responds%20at%20a%20time%20when%20growth%20is%20appearing%20to%20slow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20has%20almost%20doubled%20this%20year%2C%20although%20there%20have%20been%20wobbles%20on%20the%20way%20such%20as%20a%2010%25%20one-day%20slide%20after%20a%20wider%20market%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20will%20hold%20its%20crown%20for%20now%2C%20but%20Huang%20knows%20rivals%20are%20coming%20for%20its%20AI%20throne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-new-challengers-ai-crown-chips-earnings-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716375872000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cded47f533b039a883e2c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-new-challengers-ai-crown-chips-earnings-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nvidia's%20been%20a%20big%20winner%20of%20the%20generative%20AI%20boom%2C%20but%20rivals%20are%20trying%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20reduce%20their%20reliance%20on%20the%20%242.3%20trillion%20chip%20giant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchowdhury%40insider.com%20(Hasan%20Chowdhury)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-new-challeng