ot%20Allowed%20To%20Weaken...%26quot%3B%3A%20Poll%20Body's%20Unprecedented%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFive%20phases%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20over%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20today%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20main%20Opposition%20Congress%20over%20poll%20speeches%20by%20its%20star%20campaigners.%20This%20comes%20after%20both%20the%20parties%20had%20filed%20complaints%20against%20each%20other%2C%20flagging%20speeches%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20separate%20directions%20issued%20to%20BJP%20president%20JP%20Nadda%20and%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20said%20the%20country's%20socio-cultural%20milieu%20cannot%20become%20a%20casualty%20to%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElections%20are%20a%20process%20when%20political%20parties%20not%20only%20contest%20to%20win%2C%20but%20also%20avails%20the%20opportunity%20to%20present%20themselves%20in%20their%20ideal%20best%20for%20the%20voting%20community%20to%20experience%2C%20emulate%20and%20build%20hopes%20on.%20The%20second%20part%20constitutes%20the%20more%20precious%20heritage%20of%20Indian%20elections%20and%20our%20electoral%20democracy%20and%20this%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20be%20weakened%20by%20anyone%2C%20including%20your%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20commission%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElections%20are%20periodic%20exercises%2C%20they%20come%20and%20go%2C%20but%20political%20parties%20like%20yours%20endure%3B%20even%20more%20enduring%20preserve%20is%20India's%20socio-cultural%20milieu%3B%20Political%20parties%20are%20in%20the%20task%20of%20nurturing%20leaders%20for%20the%20country%20for%20present%20and%20future.%20They%20cannot%20afford%20to%20be%20lax%20in%20any%20manner%20in%20enforcing%20discipline%20and%20conduct%20among%20the%20cadre%20in%20the%20high%20stake%20electoral%20space%3B%20especially%20with%20reference%20to%20senior%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20poll%20body%20told%20both%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20both%20parties%20had%20approached%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20complained%20against%20each%20other's%20leaders.%20The%20poll%20body%20had%20issued%20notices%20and%20sought%20their%20responses%20on%20the%20allegations.%20In%20today's%20directions%2C%20it%20has%20rejected%20their%20defences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20letter%20to%20Mr%20Nadda%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20has%20said%20it%20expects%20BJP%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20Centre%20to%20fully%20align%20the%20campaign%20methods%20to%20the%20practical%20aspects%20of%20the%20composite%20and%20sensitive%20fabric%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20has%20directed%20the%20BJP%20to%20instruct%20all%20star%20campaigners%20to%20refrain%20from%20making%20any%20statement%20prohibited%20under%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct.%20The%20rules%2C%20it%20stressed%2C%20provide%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20party%20or%20candidate%20shall%20include%20in%20any%20activity%20which%20may%20aggravate%20existing%20difference%20or%20create%20mutual%20hatred%20or%20cause%20tension%20between%20different%20castes%20and%20communities%2C%20religious%20or%20linguistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20body%20directed%20the%20BJP%20chief%20to%20direct%20all%20star%20campaigners%20%26quot%3Bto%20not%20make%20speeches%20and%20statements%2C%20which%20may%20divide%20the%20society%26quot%3B.%20It%20also%20directed%20the%20star%20campaigners%20to%20%26quot%3Brefrain%20from%20any%20campaigning%20methods%2Futterances%20along%20religious%20communal%20lines%26quot%3B.%20The%20poll%20body%20also%20called%20for%20decorum%20in%20speeches%20by%20the%20party's%20star%20campaigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission's%20letter%20to%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20that%20it%20expects%20the%20Congress%20to%20%26quot%3Bfully%20align%20the%20campaign%20methods%20to%20the%20practical%20aspects%20of%20the%20composite%20and%20sensitive%20fabric%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20body%20asked%20the%20Congress%20chief%20to%20direct%20its%20star%20campaigners%20to%20avoid%20making%20statements%20prohibited%20under%20the%20General%20Conduct%20rules%20of%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20was%20also%20directed%20to%20ask%20Congress%20star%20campaigners%20to%20%26quot%3Bdesist%20as%20part%20of%20the%20election%20campaigning%20from%20indulging%20in%20any%20political%20propaganda%20involving%20activities%20of%20the%20Defence%20forces%20and%20not%20to%20make%20potentially%20divisive%20statements%20regarding%20socio-economic%20composition%20of%20Defence%20forces%26quot%3B.%20He%20was%20also%20told%20to%20instruct%20star%20campaigners%20%26quot%3Bthat%20they%20do%20not%20make%20statements%20which%20give%20false%20impression%20such%20as%20that%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20may%20be%20abolished%20or%20sold%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20approached%20the%20poll%20body%20over%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20allegations%20that%20the%20Opposition%20party%20wanted%20to%20redistribute%20people's%20wealth%20among%20Muslims%20and%20that%20the%20opposition%20party%20won't%20even%20spare%20married%20women's%20'mangalsutra'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20had%20flagged%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20a%20speech%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20which%20he%20alleged%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20pushing%20for%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20language%2C%20one%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20body%20had%20subsequently%20issued%20notices%20to%20Mr%20Nadda%20and%20Mr%20Kharge.%20Significantly%2C%20the%20notices%20did%20not%20name%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20or%20Mr%20Gandhi%20and%20party%20bosses%20were%20held%20responsible%20for%20speeches%20by%20star%20campaigners.%20Today's%20directions%2C%20too%2C%20do%20not%20mention%20any%20leader's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716375360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fqrn58m6_election-commission_625x300_26_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcorrect-discourse-maintain-decorum-poll-body-raps-bjp-congress-5720012%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20phases%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20over%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20today%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20main%20Opposition%20Congress%20over%20poll%20speeches%20by%20star%20campaigners%2C%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcorrect-discourse-maintain-decorum-poll-body-raps-bjp-congress-5720012%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcorrect-discourse-maintain-decorum-poll-body-raps-bjp-congress-5720012%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcorrect-discourse-maintain-decorum-poll-body-raps-bjp-congress-5720012%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prodapt%20Solutions%20aims%20to%20clock%20%241%20bn%20revenue%20in%205-6%20yrs%3A%20CEO%20Harsha%20Kumar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716375178000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F16%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1713290453-5124.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fprodapt-solutions-aims-to-clock-1-bn-revenue-in-5-6-yrs-ceo-harsha-kumar-124052200968_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prodapt%20currently%20has%20an%20employee%20base%20of%206%2C000%20globally%20of%20which%204%2C500%20are%20based%20out%20of%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-s