ahindra%20Reacts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Indore%20was%C2%A0ranked%20as%20the%20cleanest%20city%20in%20India%20for%20the%20seventh%20year%20in%20a%20row%20at%20the%20Swachh%20Survekshan%20Awards.%20The%20city%20secured%20the%20prestigious%20designation%20because%20of%20its%20well-planned%20waste%20segregation%2C%20conversion%2C%20and%20disposal%20through%20its%20public-private%20participation%20model.%20Recently%2C%C2%A0Anand%20Mahindra%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Mahindra%20Group%2C%C2%A0shared%20a%20video%20featuring%20a%20vlogger%20who%20was%20impressed%20with%20the%C2%A0exceptional%20cleanliness%20of%20Indore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%C2%A0US%20travel%20vlogger%20Max%20McFarlin%20showcased%20a%C2%A0roadside%20eatery%20in%20Indore%20and%20highlighted%20the%20simple%20measures%20undertaken%20to%20maintain%20hygiene%20and%20cleanliness.%20Mr%C2%A0McFarlin%20noted%20how%C2%A0used%20steel%20plates%20are%20placed%20in%20separate%20bins%2C%20and%20a%20small%20basin%20is%20available%20for%20people%20to%20wash%20their%20hands.%20He%20also%20appreciated%20the%20locals%20who%20are%20mindful%20of%20their%20surroundings%2C%20noticing%20how%20a%20person%20immediately%20picked%20up%20food%20after%20mistakenly%20spilling%20it%20on%20the%20street.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mahindra%20shared%20the%20video%20and%20expressed%20his%20desire%20for%20this%20cleanliness%20culture%20to%20spread%20across%20the%20nation.%C2%A0''Cannot%20help%20dreaming%3A%20If%20this%20were%20to%20be%20replicated%20throughout%20the%20country...%2C''%20he%20wrote%20while%20sharing%20the%20video.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECannot%20help%20dreaming%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIf%20this%20were%20to%20be%20replicated%20throughout%20the%20country...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPGkNSfYoA2%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FPGkNSfYoA2%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20anand%20mahindra%20(%40anandmahindra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanandmahindra%2Fstatus%2F1793140089448743333%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20a%20PTI%20report%2C%20the%20city%20spends%20Rs%20200%20crore%20annually%20on%20waste%20management.%C2%A0A%20total%20of%20850%20vehicles%20crisscross%20the%20city%20daily%20and%20collect%20692%20tonnes%20of%20wet%2C%20683%20tonnes%20of%20dry%20and%20179%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20waste%2C%20an%20official%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20video%2C%20many%20praised%20the%20city's%20culture%20and%20its%20people%20who%20know%20their%20duties%20and%20prioritize%20cleanliness.%20One%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Cleanliness%20and%20order%20are%20not%20matters%20of%20mere%20taste%20and%20upbringing%2C%20they%20are%20among%20the%20essential%20requirements%20of%20human%20beings.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20person%20commented%2C%20''India%20would%20look%20very%20different%20if%20more%20cities%20had%20residents%20like%20those%20in%20Indore%20who%20prioritize%20cleanliness.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20user%20said%2C%20''If%20this%20were%20to%20be%20replicated%20throughout%20the%20country%20then%20India%20would%20be%20the%20cleanest%20place%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Sir.%20Thanks%20for%20sharing%20such%20wonderful%20videos%20and%20awakening%20the%20people.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20Indore%20model%20is%20the%20best%20model%20of%20a%20smart%20city%20and%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Indori%20people%20take%20it%20personally%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20cleanliness%2C%20they%20make%20sure%20as%20visitors%20as%20well%2C%20we%20don't%20litter%2C%20my%20family%20there%20guided%20us%20not%20to%20litter%20on%20the%20road%20and%20stopped%20the%20car%20for%20putting%20waste%20in%20the%20