inment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbirthday-throwback-when-suhana-khan-said-she-hated-the-attention-that-she-got-being-shah-rukh-khans-daughter%2Farticleshow%2F110332933.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBJP%20Will%20Win%20305%20Seats%26quot%3B%3A%20US%20Political%20Scientist's%20Lok%20Sabha%20Poll%20Prediction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20will%20win%20305%20(%2B%2F-%2010)%20seats%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20American%20political%20scientist%20and%20global%20political%20risk%20consultant%20Ian%20Bremmer%20told%20NDTV%20Profit%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bremmer%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Eurasia%20Group%2C%20a%20risk%20and%20research%20consulting%20firm%2C%20also%20said%20the%20Indian%20general%20election%2C%20from%20a%20global%20political%20perspective%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20only%20thing%20that%20looks%20stable%20and%20consistent...everything%20else%20(including%20the%20United%20States%20election%20due%20in%20November)%20is%20problematic%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20We%20have%20an%20enormous%20amount%20of%20macro-level%20geopolitical%20uncertainty%20and%20the%20future%20of%20globalisation%20is%20not%20going%20the%20way%20companies%20want%20it%20to.%20Politics%20is%20inserting%20itself%20into%20the%20global%20marketplace...%20wars%2C%20US-China%20relations%2C%20and%20the%20US%20election%20are%20all%20a%20big%20part%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20not%20being%20managed%20well%20and%20these%20pressures%20are%20more%20negative.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20looks%20stable%20and%20consistent%2C%20politically%2C%20is%20the%20India%20election.%20Everything%20else%20looks%20problematic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20prediction%20for%20the%20Indian%20election%2C%20which%20is%20spread%20across%20seven%20phases%20and%20began%20on%20April%2019%2C%20Mr%20Bremmer%20said%20Eurasia%20Group%20research%20suggests%20the%20BJP%20will%20win%20295-315%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20party%2C%20bidding%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%2C%20won%20the%202014%20election%20with%20282%20seats%20(336%20including%20its%20NDA%20partners)%20and%20the%202019%20with%20303%20(353%20with%20NDA%20allies).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20expected%20to%20complete%20its%20hat-trick%20this%20year%20-%20a%20prediction%20backed%20by%20poll%20strategist%20Prashant%20Kishor%2C%20who%20engineered%20its%202014%20win%20-%20although%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20seen%20as%20mounting%20a%20strong%20challenge.%20Domestic%20political%20analysts%20believe%20the%202024%20battle%20could%20come%20down%20to%20one%20big%20factor%20-%20can%20the%20opposition%20eat%20into%20the%20BJP's%20fanatical%20voter%20base%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bremmer%2C%20though%2C%20stressed%20that%20his%20interest%20is%20not%20in%20the%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20interest%20is%20that%20of%20all%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20world%20(which%20includes%20polls%20in%20the%20European%20Union%20and%2C%20possibly%2C%20a%20national%20election%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom)%20India%2C%20which%20has%20the%20largest%20democracy%2C%20has%20the%20smoothest%20transition.%20There%20is%20not%20lot%20of%20uncertainty%20about%20the%20Indian%20political%20system%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bremmer%20also%20hailed%20%26quot%3Bfree%20and%20fair%2C%20and%20transparent%26quot%3B%20Indian%20electoral%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20is%20almost%20certainly%20going%20to%20win%20a%20third%20term%20on%20the%20back%20of%20pretty%20strong%20economic%20performance%20and%20consistent%20reform%20(and)%20that%2C%20in%20the%20grand%20scheme%2C%20is%20a%20very%20stabilising%20message.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20India's%20economic%20future%2C%20Mr%20Bremmer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20world%20has%20seen%20that%20India%20has%20underperformed%20for%20decades.%20India%20has%20incredible%20demographic%20weight%20and%20very%20strong%20intellectual%20capital...%20so%20many%20American%20CEOs%20come%20from%20India.%20Yet%20India%2C%20as%20an%20economy%2C%20underperformed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we%20see%20growth%20picking%20up.%20We%20see%20India%20becoming%20the%20fourth%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20likely%20next%20year%2C%20and%20the%20third%20largest%20probably%20by%202028.%20But%20we%20also%20see%20India%20becoming%20more%20powerful%20in%20terms%20of%20defining%20its%20friendship%20with%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716373380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fb1coda6g_ian-bremmer-ndtv-profit-interview_625x300_22_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fian-bremmer-ndtv-profit-interview-pm-modi-bjp-will-win-305-seats-us-political-scientists-lok-sabha-poll-prediction-5720373%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20will%20win%20305%20(%2B%2F-%2010)%20seats%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20American%20political%20scientist%20and%20global%20political%20risk%20consultant%20Ian%20Bremmer%20told%20NDTV%20Profit%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fian-bremmer-ndtv-profit-interview-pm-modi-bjp-will-win-305-seats-us-political-scientists-lok-sabha-poll-prediction-5720373%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fian-bremmer-ndtv-profit-interview-pm-modi-bjp-will-win-305-seats-us-political-scientists-lok-sabha-poll-prediction-5720373%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22amp