s-surge-in-uttar-pradesh-ndtv-battleground-5678866%5C%22%3Ehome%20stretch%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week.%20In%20about%2010%20days%2C%20the%20seven-phase%20voting%20to%20elect%20a%20new%20government%20and%20constitute%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20campaigning%20is%20central%20to%20any%20election.%20In%20mid-March%2C%20when%20the%20electoral%20race%20began%2C%20the%20incumbent%20government%20led%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20seemed%20to%20be%20in%20the%20pole%20position.%20But%20as%20the%20contest%20progressed%2C%20there%20was%20talk%20about%20the%20waning%20of%20the%20'wave'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EModified%20Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20government%20had%20started%20its%20campaigning%20much%20before%20the%20election%20schedule%20was%20announced.%20Cutouts%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20'selfie'%20points%20were%20a%20common%20sight%2C%20aimed%20at%20publicising%20the%20government's%20achievements.%20This%20was%20backed%20by%20regular%20claims%20that%20the%20development%20seen%20in%20India%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years%20was%20just%20a%20%26quot%3Btrailer%26quot%3B.%20But%20perhaps%20learning%20from%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20'India%20Shining'%20and%20the%20'feel-good%20factor'%20campaigns%20in%202004%2C%20the%20party%20modified%20its%20pitch.%20Instead%20of%20playing%20up%20the%20work%20done%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20the%20party%20chose%20to%20highlight%20how%20previous%20governments%20did%20little%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20came%20to%20welfare%20schemes%20for%20economically%20backward%20sections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneously%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20started%20talking%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20a%20strong%20government%20and%20decisive%20leadership.%20For%20instance%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20mentioned%20recently%20that%20under%20Modi's%20leadership%2C%20the%20government%20was%20able%20to%20tackle%20serious%20internal%20challenges%20like%20'Left-wing%20extremism'%20and%20the%20situation%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20India's%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%2C%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20also%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20a%20strong%20leader%20amid%20the%20emerging%20global%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-tryst-with-defection-party-hopping-as-a-constant-feature-5670240%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%20Opinion%3A%20Tryst%20with%20Defections%20--%20Party-Hopping%20As%20A%20Constant%20In%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emphasis%20on%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmodi-ki-guarantee%5C%22%3EModi%20Ki%20Guarantee%3C%2Fa%3E'%20and%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance's%20(NDA)%20target%20of%20securing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprashant-kishor-exclusive-if-bjp-doesnt-cross-370-seats-prashant-kishor-on-markets-after-poll-results-5711071%2Famp%2F1%5C%22%3E400-plus%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20reduced%20as%20party%20leaders%20increased%20direct%20attacks%20on%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies.%20Sharp%20barbs%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20family%20and%20the%20Congress's%20manifesto%20and%20promises%20followed%2C%20as%20also%20attempts%20to%20draw%20the%20party%20into%20a%20vortex%20through%20religious%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition's%20Narrative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance%20ultimately%20could%20not%20avoid%20ignoring%20the%20narrative%20the%20Opposition%20was%20building.%20Taking%20a%20cue%20from%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20Congress%20stuck%20to%20its%20script.%20It%20maintained%20that%20the%20real%20objective%20of%20the%202024%20elections%20was%20to%20protect%20the%20Constitution%2C%20charging%20that%20the%20NDA%2C%20by%20the%20admission%20of%20some%20of%20its%20own%20MPs%2C%20was%20seeking%20400-plus%20seats%20to%20alter%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20combined%20this%20attack%20with%20two%20other%20things.%20It%20alleged%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20was%20voted%20back%20to%20office%2C%20it%20would%20alter%20the%20existing%20reservation%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%2FTribes%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes.%20This%20was%20supplemented%20with%20a%20promise%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20caste%20survey%2C%20which%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20says%2C%20would%20help%20it%20recraft%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20allow%20an%20equitable%20distribution%20of%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20here%20that%20BJP-led%20parties%20were%20swift%20to%20join%20the%20discourse%2C%20prompted%20by%20concerns%20that%20the%20Opposition's%20'Constitution%20change'%20claim%20was%20getting%20traction%20and%20that%20the%20perception%20needed%20to%20be%20countered.%20The%20BJP%20launched%20a%20counter-offensive%2C%20with%20leaders%2C%20including%20PM%20Modi%2C%20reminding%20the%20electorate%20about%20the%20changes%20to%20the%20Constitution%20made%20by%20past%20Congress%20governments.%20It%20also%20alleges%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20scrap%20reservation%20for%20SC%2FSTs%20to%20facilitate%20affirmative%20action%20for%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-elections-why-a-2004-like-scenario-is-unlikely-5684511%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%20-%20Why%20A%202004-Like%20Scenario%20Is%20Unlikely%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20is%20seeking%20to%20pin%20the%20BJP%20down%20largely%20on%20bread-and-butter%20issues%20like%20price%20rise%20and%20unemployment.%20The%20alliance%20also%20promises%20to%20scrap%20the%20controversial%20Agniveer%20scheme%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%20though%2C%20a%20few%20other%20challenges%20that%20the%20world%20faces%20today%20are%20either%20missing%20from%20manifestos%20or%20are%20low-priority.%20This%20is%20true%20for%20all%20parties.%20For%20instance%2C%20there%20is%20little%20conversation%20about%2C%20say%2C%20global%20warming%20and%20the%20need%20to%20develop%20a%20green%20economy%2C%20or%20about%20tackling%20Artificial%20Intelligence.%20Parties%20should%20have%20outlined%20at%20least%20a%20basic%20plan%20for%20dealing%20with%20these%20issues%2C%20but%20they%20remain%20far%20removed%20from%20any%20serious%20discussion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(K.V.%20Prasad%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716372840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fkmh6g9lg_rahul-gandhi-narendra-modi-rahul-modi-split_625x300_21_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-how-congress-and-bjps-campaigns-have-evolved-5720178%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20mid-March%2C%20when%20the%20electoral%20race%20began%2C%20the%20incumbent%20government%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20seemed%20to%20be%20in%20the%20pole%20position.%20But%20that%20changed%20as%20the%20contest%20progressed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-how-congress-and-bjps-campaigns-have-evolved-5720178%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Strides%20Pharma%20Q4%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20declines%2024%25%20to%20Rs%2010.44%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716372833000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F07%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1709750255-5349.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fstrides-pharma-q4-results-net-profit-declines-24-to-rs-10