to%20officials%20at%20Bangkok%20Airport%2C%20where%20the%20flight%20was%20diverted.%2071%20others%20were%20injured%20on%20the%20flight%2C%20six%20of%20whom%20are%20in%20critical%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20marks%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20turbulence%20incidents%20in%20recent%20years.%20It%20is%20also%20the%20first%20death%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-show-differences-between-business-and-economy-on-singapore-airlines-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESingapore%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20flight%20since%202000.%20The%20carrier%20is%20regarded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20best%2C%20one%20of%20just%2010%20worldwide%20to%20be%20ranked%20five%20stars%20by%20Skytrax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20announced%20it%20would%20send%20five%20people%20to%20support%20the%20Singaporean%20investigation.%20It%20has%20jurisdiction%20because%20an%20American%20plane%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbritish-airways-boeing-777-new-york-london-economy-review-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing%20777%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNTSB%20has%20long%20been%20concerned%20about%20turbulence-related%20accidents%20and%20incidents%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerious%20injuries%20due%20to%20turbulence%20are%20very%20rare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fturbulence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%2C%20just%20163%20people%20were%20seriously%20injured%20by%20turbulence%20between%202009%20and%202022%20%E2%80%94%20an%20average%20of%20less%20than%2012%20people%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%2C%20129%2C%20were%20crew%20members.%20In%202022%2C%20only%20four%20passengers%20were%20seriously%20injured%20by%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20context%2