address%20character%20nuances%2C%20critiques%2C%20show%20preparation%2C%20and%20the%20mixed%20reviews.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fjason-shah-critiques-sharmin-segals-one-tone-performance-in-heeramandi%2Farticleshow%2F110331044.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Tell%20your%20star%20campaigners%20...%20'%3A%20EC%20to%20Congress%2C%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716370854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110331250%2Cimgsize-118452.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftell-star-campaigners-to-correct-discourse-maintain-decorum-ec-to-congress-bjp%2Farticleshow%2F110331046.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20has%20directed%20Bhartiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%20president%20JP%20Nadda%20and%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20to%20issue%20formal%20notes%20to%20star%20campaigners%20to%20correct%20their%20discourse%2C%20exercise%20care%20and%20maintain%20decorum.%20This%20is%20the%20Commission's%20unprecedented%20orders%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20plummeting%20quality%20of%20campaigning%20led%20by%20their%20star%20campaigners.%20The%20EC%20has%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20for%20campaigning%20along%20caste%2C%20community%2C%20language%2C%20and%20religion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTuber%20Reveals%20Gender%20Of%20Unborn%20Child%20In%20Vlog%2C%20Lands%20In%20Trouble%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20popular%20YouTuber%20has%20landed%20in%20trouble%20for%20sharing%20the%20gender%20of%20his%20unborn%20child%20on%20social%20media%20after%20getting%20sex%20determination%20test%20overseas.%20In%20a%20series%20of%20videos%2C%20Chennai-based%20Irfan%20shared%20that%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20travelled%20to%20Dubai%20to%20get%20a%20gender%20determination%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20vlogger%2C%20who%20has%204.29%20million%20followers%20on%20YouTube%2C%20revealed%20the%20child's%20gender%20in%20one%20of%20the%20videos.%20Along%20with%20footage%20of%20the%20examination%2C%20he%20revealed%20what%20the%20doctor%20had%20told%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gender%20reveal%20video%20received%20nearly%202%20million%20views%2C%20while%20the%20Dubai%20trip%20vlog%20garnered%20over%201%20million%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevealing%20the%20gender%20of%20an%20unborn%20child%20is%20illegal%20in%20India%20and%20punishable%20under%20the%20PCPNDT%20Act%20(Pre%20Conception%20%26amp%3B%20Pre%20Natal%20Diagnostic%20Techniques%20Act).%20The%20Act%20is%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20gender-based%20abortions%20and%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20and%20rights%20of%20unborn%20children.%20It%20was%20enacted%20in%201994%20to%20prevent%20female%20foeticide%20and%20address%20the%20declining%20sex%20ratio%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Health%20Department%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20him%20under%20the%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20from%20the%20Health%20Department%20says%20Irfan%20also%20posted%20videos%20of%20a%20family%20event%20in%20which%20the%20foetus'%20gender%20was%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20bid%20to%20take%20legal%20action%2C%20the%20enforcement%20officer%20has%20sent%20a%20notice%20to%20Mr%20Irfan.%20Actions%20like%20this%20could%20lead%20to%20decline%20in%20birth%20of%20girl%20babies%20not%20just%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20but%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20department%20has%20also%20written%20to%20the%20Cyber%20wing%20of%20the%20police%20to%20remove%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YouTuber%20said%20that%20he%20has%20taken%20down%20the%20video%20and%20will%20reply%20to%20the%20notice%20once%20he%20receives%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20couple%20was%20met%20with%20congratulations%20from%20many%2C%20it%20also%20sparked%20criticism%2C%20with%20some%20suggesting%20it%20could%20inadvertently%20promote%20the%20practice%20of%20traveling%20abroad%20to%20determine%20the%20sex%20of%20a%20baby.%20Others%20went%20further%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20might%20be%20a%20calculated%20move%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20subscribers%2C%20views%2C%20and%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20stringent%20measures%20against%20unauthorized%20ultrasound%20centers%20have%20significantly%20curbed%20this%20practice%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20noticeable%20improvement%20in%20India's%20sex%20ratio.%20According%20to%20data%20presented%20by%20the%20Union%20Health%20Minister%20in%20Parliament%20last%20year%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%2C%20which%20stood%20at%20876%20female%20babies%20per%201000%20male%20babies%20in%202005%2C%20has%20risen%20to%20907%20between%202018%20and%202020.%20States%20like%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20been%20commended%20for%20their%20proactive%20measures.%20Notably%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20seen%20a%20remarkable%20improvement%20in%20its%20sex%20ratio%2C%20climbing%20from%20918%20in%202015%20to%20942%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716370620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F46suasq_tamil-youtuber-irfan_625x300_22_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpopular-food-vlogger-gets-notice-for-revealing-gender-of-unborn-child-5719799%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20popular%20YouTuber%20has%20landed%20in%20trouble%20for%20sharing%20the%20gender%20of%20his%20unborn%20child%20on%20social%20media%20after%20getting%20sex%20determination%20test%20overseas.%22%2C%22author%2