20business%20school%20highlighted%20them%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fgoizueta-business-school_eightball-activity-7038601134751563776-PyFY%2F%3Ftrk%3Dpublic_profile_like_view%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20at%20least%20two%20of%20the%20students%20were%20suspended%20for%20Eightball%2C%20which%20they'd%20already%20scrapped.%20Emory%20said%20the%20duo%20violated%20the%20school's%20honor%20code%2C%20because%20students%20could%20use%20Eightball%20in%20ways%20that%20would%20breach%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJunior%20history%20major%20Benjamin%20Craver%2C%20who%20led%20marketing%20for%20the%20platform%2C%20sued%20the%20university%20on%20Friday.%20His%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24676044-16%3Fref%3D404media.co%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomplaint%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20any%20students%20used%20Eightball%20improperly%2C%20including%20to%20cheat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20highlights%20the%20tensions%20between%20universities%20eager%20to%20foster%20young%20entrepreneurs%20and%20administrative%20rules%20that%20haven't%20caught%20up%20to%20new%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmory%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20sent%20outside%20normal%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22752091e1-dc27-422e-9bfe-20bca78a4cbd%5C%22%3EExpulsion%2C%20suspension%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECraver%2C%20who%20said%20he%20had%20never%20been%20in%20trouble%20at%20Emory%2C%20partnered%20with%20a%20student%20developer%20last%20year%20to%20promote%20Eightball.%20The%20premise%20was%20simple%3A%20students%20could%20upload%20materials%20to%20a%20private%20server%20not%20accessible%20to%20other%20users%2C%20then%20use%20AI%20to%20generate%20study%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECraver%20and%20his%20cofounders%20won%20a%20business%20school%20pitch%20competition%20last%20year%2C%20and%20t