is%20also%20known%20for%20its%20hustle%20culture%2C%20evident%20from%20several%20pictures%20and%20videos%20that%20have%20captured%20people%20working%20from%20all%20sorts%20of%20odd%20places.%20Such%20posts%20have%20also%20ignited%C2%A0debates%20on%20work-life%20balance%20and%20long%20work%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20an%20X%20user%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20woman%20attending%20a%20team%20meeting%20on%20her%20laptop%C2%A0while%20shopping%20for%20footwear.%20In%20the%20image%2C%20the%20woman%20is%20seen%C2%A0holding%20a%20laptop%20while%20looking%20at%20slippers%20and%20sandals%20displayed%20at%20a%20shoe%20store.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20in%20%E2%81%A6%40peakbengaluru%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20person%20shoe%20shopping%20while%20attending%20a%20team%20meeting%20on%20her%20laptop%2C''%20the%20tweet%20by%20Karthik%20Bhaskara%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20the%20tweet%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%20in%20%E2%81%A6%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpeakbengaluru%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40peakbengaluru%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%81%A9%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20person%20shoe%20shopping%20while%20attending%20a%20team%20meeting%20on%20her%20laptop.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqHQ2omYDIl%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqHQ2omYDIl%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Karthik%20Bhaskara%20(%40Kaey_bee)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKaey_bee%2Fstatus%2F1793098483416903827%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20viral%20picture%20has%20left%20the%20internet%20divided.%20While%20some%20were%20amused%20by%20it%20and%20cracked%20jokes%2C%20others%20highlighted%20the%20negative%20impacts%20of%20such%20a%20culture%20and%20called%20it%20a%20''sad%20state%20of%20affairs.''%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Could%20have%20been%20done%20on%20the%20phone%20-%20both%20-%20the%20meeting%20and%20the%20shoe%20shopping.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20person%20commented%2C%20''This%20woman%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20companies%20are%20asking%20employees%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20office%20and%20abolish%20WFH%20policies.%20The%20problem%20is%2C%20attending%20a%20meeting%20without%20being%20present%20in%20it%20100%25%20is%20as%20good%20as%20not%20attending%20it%20at%20all..''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20user%20said%2C%20''These%20are%20the%20kind%20of%20people%20who%20made%20companies%20rescind%20Work%20From%20Home%20policies.%20Such%20a%20sad%20state.%20it%20creates%20an%20impression%20that%20people%20in%20India%20have%20no%20work%20ethics.''%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''My%20only%20thought%20is%20someone%20should%20introduce%20them%20to%20this%20unique%20invention%20called%20Bluetooth%20headphones%2C''%20joked%20a%20fourth.%20A%20fifth%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Deciding%20which%20shoe%20to%20throw%20at%20organizer%20of%20such%20useless%20meetings.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Either%20she%20is%20practising%20the%20art%20of%20'putting%20the%20best%20foot%20forward'%20or%20trying%20out%20'putting%20oneself%20in%20someone%20else's%20shoes'%20while%20being%20in%20a%20corporate%20setting%2C''%20stated%20another.%20''A%20heel-larious%20solution%20for%20work-life%20balance%2C''%20joked%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20an%20X%20user%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20man%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fpic-of-bengaluru-man-working-on-laptop-in-theatre-reignites-work-life-balance-debate-5340161%5C%22%3Eworking%20on%20a%20laptop%20inside%20a%20movie%20hall.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0A%20video%20of%20a%20man%20attending%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-police-react-to-video-of-man-working-on-laptop-while-riding-scooter-5312643%5C%22%3EZoom%20meeting%3C%2F