s%20at%20the%20wheel%2C%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20realtor%20from%20the%20city%2C%20is%20just%20four%20months%20short%20of%2018%20years%20-%20the%20minimum%20age%20required%20to%20legally%20drive%20a%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen's%20father%20has%20been%20arrested.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20owners%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20bars%20where%20the%20minor%20was%20served%20alcohol%20have%20also%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minor%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20on%20conditions%20--%20he%20has%20to%20work%20with%20traffic%20police%20in%20Yerwada%20for%2015%20days%2C%20write%20an%20essay%20on%20accidents%2C%20undergo%20treatment%20for%20his%20drinking%20habit%20and%20take%20counselling%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20bail%20decision%2C%20Pune%20Police%20have%20filed%20an%20application%20with%20the%20sessions%20court%20to%20try%20the%20juvenile%20as%20an%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECharges%20Against%20Teen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20would%20be%20tried%20and%20punished%20under%20Section%20185%20of%20the%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act%2C%20which%20deals%20with%20drink%20driving%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20act%20states%20that%20drink%20driving%20is%20a%20criminal%20offense%20if%20a%20breath%20analyzer%20test%20reveals%20that%20the%20blood%20alcohol%20concentration%20of%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20motor%20vehicle%20is%20more%20than%2030%20mg%20per%20100%20ml.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20drink%20driving%20offence%20under%20the%20act%2C%20a%20person%20can%20get%20six%20months%20of%20jail%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20For%20a%20second%20offence%2C%20you%20could%20spend%20up%20to%202%20years%20in%20jail%20and%20be%20fined%20Rs%2015%2C000%20(up%20from%20Rs%203%2C000).%20Repeat%20offenders%20might%20also%20face%20penalties%20related%20to%20their%20driving%20licenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20are%20also%20trying%20to%20prove%20a%20case%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%20where%20there%20is%20knowledge%20that%20the%20act%20could%20cause%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECharges%20Against%20Teen's%20Father%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20teen's%20father%20under%20Sections%2075%20and%2077%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act.%20These%20sections%20pertain%20to%20willful%20neglect%20of%20a%20child%20and%20providing%20intoxicating%20substances%20to%20a%20minor%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20deals%20with%20the%20willful%20neglect%20of%20a%20child%2C%20or%20exposing%20a%20child%20to%20mental%20or%20physical%20illnesses%2C%20for%20which%20punishment%20can%20stretch%20to%20a%20three-year%20jail%20term%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20The%20latter%20deals%20with%20supplying%20a%20child%20with%20intoxicating%20liquor%2C%20or%20any%20narcotics%20or%20drugs%2C%20unless%20prescribed%20by%20a%20qualified%20medical%20practitioner%2C%20and%20those%20convicted%20could%20face%20up%20to%20seven%20years%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716367500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Feoj00p2o_pune-porsche-_625x300_22_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-pune-crash-explained-charges-against-pune-builder-son-who-ran-over-2-with-porsche-5719485%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20techies%20were%20killed%20after%20a%20speeding%20Porsche%20-%20being%20driven%20by%20a%2017-year-old%20boy%20-%20hit%20their%20bike%20in%20Pune%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20incident%20has%20triggered%20massive%20anger%2Cwith%20many%20blaming%20lax%20laws%20for%20deaths%20due%20to%20rash%20driving%20and%20minors%20on%20the%20wheels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-pune-crash-explained-charges-against-pune-builder-son-who-ran-over-2-with-porsche-5719