el-has-a-manchester-united-themed-suite-for-football-fans-5719210%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvideo-this-dubai-hotel-has-a-manchester-united-themed-suite-for-football-fans-5719210%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Santosh%20-%20Shahana%20Delivers%20A%20Performance%20Of%20Astounding%20Depth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20cop%20drama%20receives%20a%20pronounced%20makeover%20in%20%3Ci%3ESantosh%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20British-Indian%20director%20Sandhya%20Suri's%20first%20fiction%20feature%2C%20a%20Hindi-language%20film%20featuring%20Shahana%20Goswami%20and%20Sunita%20Rajwar%20in%20roles%20that%20neither%20has%20played%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20forays%20into%20the%20rural%20boondocks%20of%20North%20India%20and%20examines%20religious%20prejudice%2C%20caste%20discrimination%2C%20abuse%20of%20power%2C%20custodial%20torture%20and%20gender%20dynamics%20in%20a%20police%20station%20and%20in%20the%20communities%20that%20it%20serves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuri's%20percipient%20script%20puts%20two%20policewomen%20-%20one%20a%20hardened%20pro%20who%20has%20seen%20it%20all%2C%20the%20other%20a%20rookie%20struggling%20with%20half-truths%20and%20undisguised%20lies%20-%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20tale%20that%20delves%20into%20a%20broken%20system%20that%20is%20manipulated%20at%20will%20by%20those%20that%20wield%20power%2C%20be%20it%20social%2C%20political%20or%20administrative.%20It%20is%20they%20who%20determined%20the%20substance%20and%20course%20of%20justice%20and%20the%20police%20force%20plays%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recently%20widowed%20woman%2C%20Santosh%20Saini%20(Shahana%20Goswami)%2C%20is%20inducted%20into%20the%20force%20on%20compassionate%20grounds.%20Before%20she%20can%20find%20her%20feet%20in%20the%20job%2C%20the%20constable%20finds%20herself%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20sensitive%20crime%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Dalit%20girl%20has%20been%20raped%20and%20murdered%20in%20a%20village.%20The%20probe%20is%20led%20by%20a%20tough%20female%20inspector%2C%20Geeta%20Sharma%20(Sunita%20Rajwar)%20-%20she%20is%20addressed%20as%20'Sharmaji'%20-%20who%20is%20not%20averse%20to%20getting%20her%20hands%20dirty%20in%20the%20cesspool%20that%20surrounds%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ESantosh%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20set%20in%20a%20state%20called%20Chirag%20Pradesh.%20The%20towns%20in%20which%20the%20story%20plays%20out%20-%20Nehrat%2C%20Mapur%2C%20Madrabad%2C%20Ghazaliabad%2C%20Machogarh%20-%20bear%20fictitious%20names.%20Besides%20the%20fact%20that%20these%20places%20have%20parallels%20in%20the%20real%20world%2C%20everything%20in%20%3Ci%3ESantosh%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20rooted%20in%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20police%20procedural%20that%20isn't%20limited%20by%20genre%20conventions.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20defined%20by%20its%20steadfast%20abjuration%20of%20the%20norms%20of%20the%20form.%20Santosh%20is%20a%20slow-burning%20and%20trenchant%20commentary%20on%20the%20ills%20of%20a%20society%20where%20biases%20of%20many%20kinds%20run%20rampant%20often%20with%20horrific%20consequences.%20But%20life%20goes%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ESantosh%3C%2Fi%3E%20follows%20both%20the%20personal%20and%20the%20collective%20with%20equal%20rigour%2C%20revealing%20the%20fault%20lines%20that%20the%20new%20policewoman%20must%20understand%20and%20deal%20with%20as%20her%20superior%2C%20a%20woman%20who%20has%20years%20of%20experience%20under%20her%20belt%2C%20not%20only%20does%20a%20bit%20of%20hand-holding%20but%20also%20goes%20out%20of%20her%20way%20to%20make%20the%20newbie's%20work%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bonding%20that%20develops%20between%20the%20two%20women%20in%20a%20male-dominated%20force%20also%20brings%20out%20the%20marked%20divergence%20in%20the%20approaches%20of%20the%20two%20cops.%20Santosh%20is%20an%20outsider.%20She%20is%20barely%20accepted%20by%20the%20men%20in%20the%20police%20station.%20But%20she%20soldiers%20on.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Sharma%20is%20the%20boss.%20The%20unflappable%20lady%20calls%20the%20shots.%20She%20seems%20keen%20to%20mould%20Santosh%20in%20her%20own%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20grief%20of%20losing%20her%20policeman-husband%20in%20the%20line%20of%20duty%2C%20Santosh%20has%20to%20reckon%20with%20the%20apathy%20and%20cynicism%20of%20the%20men%2C%20in%20uniform%20and%20otherwise%2C%20she%20works%20with.%20She%20learns%20the%20ropes%20pretty%20quickly%20but%20cannot%20shrug%20off%20the%20sense%20of%20guilt%20and%20frustration%20that%20comes%20with%20the%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20illiterate%20Dalit%20man%20approaches%20the%20cops%20to%20complain%20that%20his%20only%20daughter%20is%20missing.%20He%20is%20all%20but%20shooed%20away.%20Santosh%20steps%20in%20and%20offers%20to%20help%20the%20hapless%20father.%20But%20how%20far%20can%20she%20go%20in%20the%20face%20of%20her%20male%20colleagues'%20all-round%20and%20ingrained%20reluctance%20to%20serve%20the%20dispossessed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20girl%20arrives%20at%20the%20police%20station%20to%20lodge%20a%20complaint%20about%20a%20perfidious%20boyfriend.%20The%20girl's%20father%2C%20who%20has%20the%20means%20that%20missing%20Dalit%20girl's%20father%20does%20not%2C%20bribes%20one%20of%20the%20cops%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20mete%20out%20instant%20punishment%20to%20the%20'erring'%20boy.%20Santosh%20can%20only%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20injustices%20that%20the%20men%20under%20her%20perpetrate%20with%20impunity%2C%20Sharma%20comes%20across%20as%20a%20woman%20who%20espouses%20the%20right%20principals.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20case%20proceeds%20and%20Santosh%20descends%20deeper%20and%20deeper%20into%20moral%20grey%20areas%2C%20she%20begins%20to%20figure%20out%20that%20nobody%20in%20the%20police%20force%2C%20not%20even%20her%20apparently%20benign%20mentor%2C%20is%20free%20of%20stains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaste%20oppression%20and%20misogyny%20are%20hidden%20in%20plain%20sight%20in%20Santosh.%20The%20film%20also%20underscores%20the%20casual%20manner%20in%20which%20religious%20fissures%20are%20normalised%20in%20a%20divided%20society.%20%26quot%3BIt%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20unperturbed%20Sharma%20says%20to%20Santosh%20when%20the%20investigation%20takes%20an%20avoidable%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20an%20indefensible%20act%2C%20Sharma%20reminds%20Santosh%20that%20this%20country%20has%20two%20types%20of%20%26quot%3Buntouchables%26quot%3B%20-%20those%20that%20you%20do%20not%20touch%20and%20those%20that%20you%20cannot%20touch.%20The%20battle%20between%20the%20two%20is%20not%20only%20unequal%20but%20unending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20repeatedly%20defiled%20well%20in%20a%20Dalit%20village%20is%20the%20site%20of%20continuing%20upper%20caste%20tyranny.%20A%20mutilated%20corpse%20is%20found%20in%20it.%20A%20decomposed%20cat%20and%20a%20dead%20canine%20are%20thrown%20into%20it.%20The%20community%20that%20uses%20the%20well%20is%20angry%20but%20powerless.%20They%20know%20they%20will%20have%20to%20live%20with%20being%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20because%20the%20impervious%20upper%20caste%20men%20of%20the%20village%20can%20get%20away%20with%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ESantosh%3C%2Fi%3E%20has%20no%20background%20score.%20Two%20songs%20that%20play%20on%20the%20audio%20system%20of%20the%20Inspector%20Sharma's%20official%20vehicle%20are%20meant%20to%20break%20the%20solemnity%20of%20two%20policewomen's%20work.%20In%20the%20silences%2C%20the%20ambient%20sounds%2C%20especially%20the%20thwack%20of%20an%20off-camera%20police%20baton%20landing%20an%20accused's%20back%2C%20become%20all%20the%20more%20chilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahana%20Goswami%20delivers%20a%20performance%20of%20astounding%20emotional%20depth.%20She%20brings%20out%20the%20inner%20turmoil%20of%20the%20titular%20character%2C%20an%20ingenue%20who%20must%20find%20her%20way%20around%20in%20a%20world%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20corruption%20and%20exploitation%2C%20with%20restraint.%20The%20means%