iting%20for%20that%20mango%20tree%20to%20bear%20fruit!%20Using%20grafted%20fruit%20plants%2C%20she%20has%20managed%20to%20grow%20over%20six%20varieties%20of%20mango.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20year%2C%20flowers%20will%20drop%20as%20the%20plant%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20fruit.%20Remove%20the%20flowers%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20plant.%20Typically%2C%20you%20will%20not%20get%20any%20fruits%20in%20the%20first%20year%2C%20maybe%20two%20in%20the%20second%2C%20five%20to%20six%20in%20the%20third%20and%20so%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20gardener.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushma%20grows%20all%20her%20fruits%20in%2010-16%20inch%20pots%20on%20her%20terrace%2C%20as%20she%20stays%20in%20a%20rented%20apartment%20and%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20for%20her%20to%20transport%20them%2C%20should%20the%20need%20arise.%20She%20would%20get%20a%20much%20better%20yield%20with%20bigger%20pots%2C%20she%20asserts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Bengaluru%20resident%20is%20extremely%20satisfied%20with%20the%20yield%20that%20her%20terrace%20garden%20produces.%20With%20over%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343071%2Fhow-to-grow-strawberries-dragon-fruit-turmeric-terrace-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E20%20vegetables%20and%2070%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20her%20family%20eats%20what%20they%20grow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20very%20happy%20today%20as%20I%20found%20my%20passion%20in%20gardening.%20It%20gives%20me%20immense%20satisfaction.%20The%20happiness%20I%20feel%20when%20a%20flower%20blooms%20is%20similar%20to%20what%20I%20feel%20when%20my%20son%20speaks%20a%20word%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20mother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FI