20and%20me)%20to%20move%20to%20China%20as%20he%20felt%20that%20it%20was%20a%20great%20place%20to%20start%20a%20venture.%20We%20moved%20there%20for%20a%20year%20in%202010%20but%20realised%20that%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20feasible%20to%20scale%20a%20business%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sreejith%2C%20COO%20of%20True%20Elements%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20learnt%20an%20important%20lesson%20in%20China.%20The%20Chinese%20had%20very%20good%20food%20habits.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20cook%20food%20correctly%2C%20eat%20right%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20consume%20food%20at%20the%20right%20time.%20We%20do%20all%20three%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20realisation%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20health-related%20challenges%20at%20their%20house%20solidified%20the%20need%20to%20create%20a%20change%20in%20this%20sector.%20Puru%20lost%20his%20father%20to%20cancer%2C%20while%20Sreejith%E2%80%99s%20father-in-law%20died%20of%20heart%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20as%20a%20family%20that%20we%20never%20gave%20importance%20to%20preventative%20healthcare.%20We%20only%20take%20care%20of%20our%20health%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20too%20late%2C%20or%20when%20some%20parameters%20are%20off%20the%20charts.%20Why%20do%20we%20react%20so%20late%3F%20We%20could%20have%20taken%20care%20of%20it%20earlier%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru%2C%20CEO%20of%20True%20Elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20five%20years%20of%20brainstorming%2C%20Puru%20quit%20his%20job%20in%202011%20and%20started%20working%20on%20creating%20awareness%20about%20health%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20consuming%20the%20right%20food.%20The%20first%20company%20that%20the%20duo%20started%20was%20called%20%E2%80%98Healthy%20World%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20aggregator%20of%20healthy%20food%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20people%20take%20care%20of%20their%20health%20before%20it%20gets%20too%20late.%20We%20started%20by%20creating%20awareness%20and%20a%20market%20for%20brands%20that%20sell%20healthy%20foods%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru%20with%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20made%20a%20list%20of%20such%20brands%20and%20then%20started%20approaching%20them%2C%20offering%20to%20create%20a%20distribution%20channel%20for%20them.%20Puru%20leveraged%20his%20FMCG%20(Fast%20Moving%20Consumer%20Goods)%20background%20to%20create%20a%20distribution%20framework%20for%20%E2%80%98good%20for%20you%E2%80%99%20brands%2C%20while%20Sreejith%20used%20his%20HR%20experience%20to%20get%20entry%20into%20corporate%20cafeterias.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20started%20by%20setting%20up%20kiosks%20at%20IT%20companies%20with%20a%20mission%20to%20change%20their%20snacking%20choices.%20They%20also%20created%20healthy%20hampers%20for%20events%20like%20marathons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20months%20after%20launching%20the%20venture%2C%20Sreejith%20also%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20scale%20the%20business.%20However%2C%20the%20duo%20faced%20their%20first%20failure%2C%20as%20they%20realised%20that%20the%20corporate%20kiosk%20model%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20number%20of%20people%20opting%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325105%2Fhyderabad-entrepreneur-raju-bhupati-makes-affordable-troo-good-millet-snacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20snacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20very%20less.%20Those%20who%20wanted%20to%20eat%20healthy%20got%20their%20%3Cem%3Edabbas%20%3C%2Fem%3Efrom%20home.%20People%20coming%20to%20cafeterias%20weren%E2%80%99t%20interested%20in%20their%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sreejith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20months%20in%20and%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20down%2C%20they%20faced%20a%20trying%20ti