and%20variety%2C%20as%20well%20as%20seeking%20the%20appropriate%20support%2C%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRemember%2C%20different%20climates%20require%20different%20management%20practices%20and%20techniques.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20methods%20used%20in%20South%20India%20differ%20from%20those%20used%20in%20Central%20India%20where%20I%20am%20based.%20Expecting%20similar%20results%20from%20cheaper%20plants%20without%20considering%20these%20factors%20may%20lead%20to%20disappointment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20Pictures%20Credit%3A%20Harshit%20Godha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715777750000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350000%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Urban%20farmer%20Harshit%20Godha%20took%20inspiration%20from%20Israeli%20farmers%20growing%20avocadoes%20and%20has%20successfully%20grown%20the%20fruit%20in%20India.%20He%20shares%20how%20you%20can%20grow%20them%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350000%2Fhow-to-grow-avocado-in-india-urban-farmer-harshit-godha-imports-saplings-from-israel-teaches-farming%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%202%20Cr%20Salary%20to%202%20Million%20Followers%3A%20How%20%E2%80%98FoodPharmer%E2%80%99%20Started%20A%20Food%20Revolution%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20grab%20a%20food%20item%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20our%20instinct%20is%20often%20to%20check%20the%20expiry%20date.%20But%20do%20we%20also%20spare%20just%20a%20couple%20more%20minutes%20to%20scan%20the%20ingredient%20list%3F%20These%20extra%20moments%20could%20be%20crucial%2C%20shaping%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20food%20we%E2%80%99re%20putting%20in