nt%20of%20sugar%20in%20the%20drink%2C%20yet%20calling%20itself%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20could%20cause%20diabetes.%20The%20video%20went%20viral%20across%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20leading%20to%20legal%20trouble%20for%20the%20former%20consultant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMondelez%20sent%20him%20a%20legal%20notice%20asking%20him%20to%20take%20down%20the%20video.%20Left%20with%20no%20choice%2C%20Revant%20took%20it%20down%20and%20issued%20a%20statement.%20However%2C%20he%20had%20achieved%20what%20he%20set%20out%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20create%20awareness%20among%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStay%20away%20from%20sugary%20drinks%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20legal%20notice%2C%20Cadbury%20reduced%20the%20quantity%20of%20added%20sugar%20in%20Bournvita%20by%2014.4%20percent%20in%20December%202023%2C%20validating%20the%20content%20creator%E2%80%99s%20efforts.%20The%20Central%20Government%20also%20directed%20e-commerce%20firms%20to%20remove%20Bournvita%20and%20other%20such%20drinks%20from%20the%20health%20drinks%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20product%20that%20reduced%20its%20sugar%20content%20by%2022%20percent%20was%20%E2%80%98Maggi%20rich%20tomato%20ketchup%E2%80%99.%20Revant%20made%20a%20video%20highlighting%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20product%20had%20more%20sugar%20than%20tomatoes!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20actions%20have%20been%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20content%20creator%2C%20who%20has%20since%20educated%20Indians%20on%20many%20other%20packaged%20products.%20His%20problem%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20with%20the%20false%20marketing%20by%20companies%2C%20which%20promise%20nutrition%2C%20strength%20and%20more%20for%20your%20child%2C%20when%20actually%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20filled%20with%20sugar.%20His%20problem%20is%20not%20with%20chocolates%20or%20Coke%20as%20much%20as%20with%20drinks%20like%20Bournvita%20and%20biscuits%20that%20are%20fed%20to%20children%2